      <description>Valentine&amp;#8217;s Day is behind us for another year, and most of us sports enthusiasts are tuned into the Winter Olympics being held in and around Vancouver, British Columbia.  Hosting visitors from around the world, there are bound to be some Funny Questions About Canada.
If you&amp;#8217;re happy in a relationship you wouldn&amp;#8217;t think about flirting with someone [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/datepad-blog-follow-the-datepad-journey/Datepad_Blog_-_Follow_the_Datepad_journey-Must_Read_Dating_Articles_-_February_22_Edition.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Valentine&#8217;s Day is behind us for another year, and most of us sports enthusiasts are tuned into the Winter Olympics being held in and around Vancouver, British Columbia.  Hosting visitors from around the world, there are bound to be some <a title="Canada" href="http://www.datepad.com/articles/funny-questions-about-canada/" target="_blank">Funny Questions About Canada</a>.</p>
<p>If you&#8217;re happy in a relationship you wouldn&#8217;t think about flirting with someone else, would you?  Some consider it a sport, but it you don&#8217;t know where to draw the line, you could find yourself acting out <a title="Dangerous" href="http://www.datepad.com/articles/dangerous-relationship-behaviors-not-quite-cheating/" target="_blank">Dangerous Relationship Behavior</a>.</p>
<p><a title="Gigolo" href="http://www.datepad.com/articles/americas-first-legal-gigolo/" target="_blank">America’s First Legal Gigolo</a> examines America&#8217;s first legal prostidude (yes, that&#8217;s spelled correctly!), while <a title="Fashion" href="http://www.datepad.com/articles/7-worst-fashion-trends-ever/" target="_blank">7 Worst Fashion Trends Ever</a> takes a lighthearted look at what we&#8217;ve chosen to to put on our bodies over the years.  It seems that some of it should&#8217;ve gone straight into the garbage!</p>
<p>That&#8217;s all for this week, more next Monday.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
