      <description>We continued the countdown to Valentine&amp;#8217;s Day with Greeting Cards, E-Cards and E-Videos and Feeling Like The Dating Cupid Forgot About You? For a different take on the hearts, flowers and chocolates have a lookat When V-Day Feels More Like C-Day.
Ever wondered if your guy/gal was really working late?  Dangerous Relationship Behaviours; Snooping examines whether [...]&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/datepad-blog-follow-the-datepad-journey/Datepad_Blog_-_Follow_the_Datepad_journey-Must_Read_Dating_Articles_-_February_16_Edition.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>We continued the countdown to Valentine&#8217;s Day with <a title="Cards and videos" href="http://www.datepad.com/articles/greeting-cards-e-cards-and-e-videos/" target="_blank">Greeting Cards, E-Cards and E-Videos</a> and <a title="Dating Cupid" href="http://www.datepad.com/articles/feeling-like-the-dating-cupid-forgot-about-you/" target="_blank">Feeling Like The Dating Cupid Forgot About You?</a> For a different take on the hearts, flowers and chocolates have a lookat <a title="V-Day or C-Day" href="http://www.datepad.com/articles/when-v-day-feels-more-like-c-day/" target="_blank">When V-Day Feels More Like C-Day</a>.</p>
<p>Ever wondered if your guy/gal was <em>really </em>working late?  <a title="Snooping" href="http://www.datepad.com/articles/dangerous-relationship-behaviors-snooping/" target="_blank">Dangerous Relationship Behaviours; Snooping</a> examines whether to snoop or not.</p>
<p>Our lives are made up of decisions; we make them every single day.  When it comes to sex, there are some <a title="Decision" href="http://www.datepad.com/articles/bad-sex-decisions-that-are-totally-worth-making/" target="_blank">Bad Sex Decisions That Are Totally Worth Making</a>.  But if all that sexy decision making is just too much to handle, find out <a title="Abstinence" href="http://www.datepad.com/articles/why-abstinence-is-hot/" target="_blank">Why Abstinence Is Hot</a>.  No, really!</p>
<p>Anyone who&#8217;s half of a loving couple wouldn&#8217;t trade it for the world, myself included, but that doesn&#8217;t mean there aren&#8217;t <a title="Being single" href="http://www.datepad.com/articles/things-i-miss-about-being-single/" target="_blank">Things I Miss About Being Single</a>.</p>
<p>And finally, for an interesting take on the sexes read <a title="Gender" href="http://www.datepad.com/articles/gender-switch-male-pms-and-female-ejaculation/" target="_blank">Gender Switch; Male PMS and Female Ejaculation</a>.  Who knew??!!</p>
<p>That&#8217;s the condensed version of last week&#8217;s articles.  More next week!</p>
]]></content:encoded>
